HEADWORD: Wayside
<hw>Way"side`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The side of the way;
the edge or border of a road or path.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wayside</ent>⟦br⟧

